Source: matrixio-odas
Section: embedded
Priority: optional
Maintainer: MATRIX Labs <info@matrix.one>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), cmake, libmatrixio-creator-hal-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://github.com/matrix-io/odas

Package: matrixio-odas
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},matrixio-creator-init,matrixio-kernel-modules
Description: ODAS stands for Open embeddeD Audition System. This is a library dedicated to perform sound source localization, tracking, separation and post-filtering. ODAS is coded entirely in C, for more portability, and is optimized to run easily on low-cost embedded hardware. ODAS is free and open source.
